@page "/favorites"

<PageTitle>Favorites</PageTitle>

<div class="space-y-6">
    <header class="space-y-3">
        <div>
            <p class="text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.28em] text-signal-600">Cutover</p>
            <h1 class="font-display text-4xl text-cinder-950 sm:text-5xl">Legacy favorites page retired</h1>
        </div>
        <p class="max-w-5xl text-base leading-8 text-cinder-800">
            Favorite node management is no longer owned by the server-rendered UI. It is being moved fully to the
            browser-first client and API-backed preference flow.
        </p>
    </header>

    <section class="grid gap-4 xl:grid-cols-[1.05fr_0.95fr]">
        <article class="liquid-panel rounded-[1.6rem] p-6">
            <h2 class="font-display text-3xl text-cinder-950">Moved off the server page</h2>
            <ul class="mt-5 list-disc space-y-2 pl-5 text-cinder-800/84">
                <li>Favorite-node list refresh through projection change notifications.</li>
                <li>Inline remove actions backed by the server-rendered page.</li>
                <li>Modal-driven node detail drill-down from the legacy UI.</li>
            </ul>
        </article>

        <article class="liquid-panel rounded-[1.6rem] p-6">
            <h2 class="font-display text-3xl text-cinder-950">Temporary server path</h2>
            <p class="mt-4 text-cinder-800/82">
                This route stays only as a cutover marker while the remaining server-rendered pages are removed.
            </p>
            <div class="mt-6 flex flex-wrap gap-3">
                <a href="/" class="liquid-button inline-flex items-center rounded-full px-4 py-2 text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.14em]">Dashboard</a>
                <a href="/nodes" class="liquid-button inline-flex items-center rounded-full px-4 py-2 text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.14em]">Nodes</a>
                <a href="/topics" class="liquid-button inline-flex items-center rounded-full px-4 py-2 text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.14em]">Topics</a>
            </div>
        </article>
    </section>
</div>
